  </h2>
  <section id="bio">
    <h1></h1><div class="line"></div>
    <p>My hobby is drawing. I love to draw with different colours. I mostly draw pictures of people, animals and birds. I use crayons, pencils, colour pencils etc to draw pictures. For me, drawing is creation. Just like when an author writes a fiction book, they're creating life through words, an entire world within the pages of their book.</p>
